00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:10,740
And what your mind does when
当你把脑袋投向雕塑时

317
00:19:10,740 --> 00:19:13,440
it's looking at the sculpture, when
当你把脑袋投向雕塑时，正与之对话

318
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:17,740
it is in conversation with the sculpture, it is imagining what happens before
当你与雕塑对话时，脑袋在想象之前的情景

