这些图画几乎像视觉辅助手。

336
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:24,720
So when the priest is talking about the stories of the Bible, he's using these,
于是当牧师讲述圣经故事时，他就用这些图画。

337
00:20:25,700 --> 00:20:28,780
um, pictures to illustrate his point.
嗯，图画来说明他的观点。

338
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:32,300
Because remember, at this point, most people are illiterate.
因为记得，在这一点上，大多数人还是文盲。

339
00:20:32,820 --> 00:20:34,420
Because of these stained glass windows,
因为这些彩绘玻璃窗。

