Okay? Does that make sense? You're not here to participate.
好的？这样说通吗？你来这里不是为了参与。

353
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:19,300
You're here to submit.
你来这里是为了投降。

354
00:21:21,860 --> 00:21:24,320
All right? So as you can see, this is a church.
好的？正如你所见，这是一座教堂。

355
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:26,160
You can see how the light comes in.
你可以看到光线是如何进入的。

356
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:28,260
And it blinds you.
它照得你眼花。

357
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:31,860
All right? And it's hard for you to really participate
好吧？你很难真正参与。

358
00:21:32,390 --> 00:21:34,380
in the artwork.
在画作中。

359
00:21:34,720 --> 00:21:37,800
So this is the idea of medieval Christianity.
于是这就是中世纪基督教的概念。

360
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:41,540
The idea that you, through artwork,
通过画作，你可以感受到的概念。

361
